data.description: Wonderful 3 bed/2.5 bath SW Medford home near South Medford High! This home features a spacious kitchen w/granite counters, brand new Frigidaire Gallery stainless steel appliances, lots of counter space, breakfast bar & pantry. The kitchen leads to the dining area w/slider leading to the back patio. The large living room has several windows for natural light. Upstairs you will find the primary bedroom w/a walk in closet, a double vanity in the primary bathroom & lots of windows! Two more bedrooms, a full bath & laundry room are also upstairs. The laundry has lots of cabinets for storage! There are so many upgrades throughout this home including new floors, new light fixtures & new appliances! There is also great storage-linen closets, pantry, extra cabinets,the garage, & even space under the stairs!  Outside is a lovely back yard w/a patio & storage shed. The front of the house also features a covered front porch to enjoy the outdoors!  Come tour this home today!
